### Preflight CORS CompatibilityAttributes
OPTIONS {{compatBase}}/api/users/{{userId}}/compatibility-attributes
Origin: {{compatBase}}

### Obter atributos de compatibilidade (GET)
GET {{compatBase}}/api/users/{{userId}}/compatibility-attributes
Origin: {{compatBase}}

### Atualizar/Inserir atributos de compatibilidade (PUT)
PUT {{compatBase}}/api/users/{{userId}}/compatibility-attributes
Content-Type: application/json
Origin: {{compatBase}}

{
  "mbtiType": "INTJ-F"
}

### Preflight CORS Invites
OPTIONS {{compatBase}}/api/invites
Origin: {{compatBase}}

### Listar convites (GET)
GET {{compatBase}}/api/invites
Origin: {{compatBase}}

### Criar convite (POST)
POST {{compatBase}}/api/invites
Content-Type: application/json
Origin: {{compatBase}}

{
  "senderId": {{senderId}},
  "recipientId": {{recipientId}}
}
